	* : commit d51689f572e544759632fa2f9ca0209a843d4452 Author: Ludovic
	Court√®s <ludo@chbouib.org> Date:   Thu May 31 00:28:19 2007 +0200

2007-05-31  Ludovic Court√®s <ludo@chbouib.org>

