2002-11-12  Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* includes/gnutls/extra.h, lib/gnutls_int.h: The
	gnutls_openpgp_recv_key_func() callback function now accepts a key
	fingerprint, instead of the key id.

