	lib/gnutls_handshake.c, lib/gnutls_handshake.h, lib/gnutls_int.h,
	lib/gnutls_priority.c, lib/gnutls_v2_compat.c, src/serv.c: Updated
	Ciphersuite selection algorithm.  Added internal representation of
	x509 structures.

