2001-02-01  Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* lib/gnutls.c, lib/gnutls_cipher.c: gnutls_send_int() no longer
	sends the packets with 2 Write() calls.  One Write() call is enough
	for everybody!

